{
  "texts": [
    "Although data-driven models can identify low-level patterns within motion sensor data, our goal is to leverage the common-sense knowledge implicitly encoded in LLMs.",
    "Preliminary experiments suggested that using LLMs with datasets mostly based on motion sensors can not reliably recognize ADLs.4.1.1 MARBLE.",
    "The MARBLE dataset [4] includes data collected from 12 subjects in both single and multi-inhabitant scenarios.",
    "The dataset was collected using the following environmental sensors: magnetic sensors to capture the opening and closing of various drawers and cabinets, pressure sensors to detect when a subject was sitting at the dining table or on the sofa in the living room, and smart plugs to monitor the usage of the stove and television.",
    "Additionally, the dataset includes data from an Android application on the user's smartphone, which automatically detects incoming and outgoing phone calls."
  ]
}